Generating C++ headers
sdkdir/sdk/bin/header.py --cachedir=<path> -o <outputfilename.h> <filename.idl>

Generating typelibs
sdkdir/sdk/bin/typelib.py --cachedir=<path> -o <oputputfilename.xpt> <filename.idl>

